{
  "stem": "3103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One sight at my childhood-- which maybe when I was 11, 12 years old, there was one street the Jews walked and one street the Gentiles walked.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember my grandfather once coming home in the evening when I was visiting, he was beat up by three Gentile boys, and that's all my memory because I didn't live there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just came that time visiting, and I just heard what they used to tell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if I went to this-- I mean to the [POLISH] with my aunt, the younger one, Sarah, and the girlfriends, we used to walk on the side where the Jewish people were suppose to walk.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You wouldn't want to do it because you took a chance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very much so because there was announcement from the government, you know, for the night to cover up the windows, seal them up so they won't see in the light.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that they gave us warning of preparing in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go to the grocery, buy enough flour, sugar, bread so you have at least for a week.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm very much aware of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and that was very quick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a week.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My uncle, Mendel, who lives now in Australia actually came from Sosnowiec to us because he thought it's going to be a safer place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the 3rd one of September, the early morning, my father woke up and he said, kids, get dressed and it's time to go to a smaller town.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We will stay overnight, and we come back because the Germans are beginning to bombard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39, September 3.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, dress yourself, take what you can, and we go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the time, it was such a panic that my mother grabbed a few rolls from the refrigerator, whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
